  "body": "### Description\n\nHi! At my company we send logs to graylog using the kafka transport with our spring applications, I'm evaluating the use of quarkus and didn't find any documentation on how to setup quarkus to use kafka as transport on the [Centralized Log Management Page](https://quarkus.io/guides/centralized-log-management). I wonder if it's possible to use quarkus in this scenario. \r\n\r\nThanks for the amazing job with this framework!\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\nAdd documentation on how to use different transports when using centralized logging with quarkus",
